    <text id="A5047T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>George Baylor writes to his sister about clothes and food he wants her to send to
                    him.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1862-06-12">June the 12 1862</date>
                        <name type="place">Camp near <unclear>Wirs Cove</unclear></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Sister</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>It has been so long since I have written to you I dont know when was the last
                    time. I wrote to <unclear>Est</unclear> yesterday <orig reg="evening"
                    >eavining</orig> and I believe I gave her all the news I <orig reg="knew"
                    >knowed</orig> only I want you to send me a shirt and a pair of cotton pants in
                    the same size <orig reg="of">off</orig> my Sunday pants. I would like to have
                    them as soon as you can send them. I <unclear>
                        <orig reg="ought">ort</orig>
                    </unclear> to have a Calico shirt at home I think. I would like to have
                    something good to <hi rend="underline">Eat</hi>
                    <pb n="2"/> if you could send something down. I have <orig reg="gotten"
                    >goten</orig> tired of bread and meat. I want to get home about <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    time if I can.</p>

                <p>I have nothing more to write this time.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute/>
                    <signed>George W. Baylor</signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">
                        <name type="recipient">to Mary C. Baylor</name>
                    </seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
